high_descs: Turn right and begin walking to the toilet, then turn left and walk up to the left side of the tub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap that is resting on the corner of the tub.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Place the bar of soap into the sink basin and use the water to clean the bar of soap., then pick it back up
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn left to face the small green trash can.
Place the clean bar of soap into the small green trash can.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bar of soap into a small green trash can.

high_descs: Turn right, then left, then face the black table on your left.
Pick up the pink soap on the tub on the right.
Turn around and head towards the sink.
Put the soap in the sink, run water, turn it off, then pick up the pink soap.
Turn right, then face left to see the green trash-can.
Throw the soap in the green trash-can.
Turn around to face the toilet then go left towards the tub. Then turn to the right to face the table.
Pick up the soap that is on the edge of the tub.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the soap in the sink and turn on the water. Turn it off and pick the soap back up.
Walk to the right and turn to face the green garbage can next to the sink.
Throw the soap away into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To use the soap and throw it away.
